{"tid":2106522,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"男朋友阿媽條仔好on9","createTime":"2020-07-13T11:35:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-13T19:36:21.000Z","uid":222055,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"6afaf904da947a4617c285e960074b5c63c825f1","tid":2106522,"uid":222055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T11:35:38.000Z","msg":"事緣係我有時星期六日會去男朋友屋企度過一晚夜，咁我男朋友係同佢阿媽一齊住嘅，咁佢媽都冇唔會介意我去過夜嘅，因為我同佢媽相處都無問題、有計傾<br />\n直到佢媽識左個男朋友，佢媽條仔搬左入去同佢地住，本身呢都好地地，之後呢我成日覺得佢媽條仔係到搞搞陣，因為自從條友入左去同佢地住之後，佢媽對我態度就唔同左，可以肯定呢條友一定有講鳩我"},{"pid":"a21676fed0b50700cd73a1145dfe601094b1bed8","tid":2106522,"uid":30604,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T11:37:47.000Z","msg":"咁就代表佢戇鳩？定你戇鳩呀？"},{"pid":"439ca49d2ca6d979fb51fb3acde138c0934bc087","tid":2106522,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T11:38:26.000Z","msg":"屌到佢條仔求你原諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7d96c1440e603a91c3629432bd1c2b2f9c10190","tid":2106522,"uid":222055,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"a21676fed0b50700cd73a1145dfe601094b1bed8","tid":2106522,"uid":30604,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T11:37:47.000Z","msg":"咁就代表佢戇鳩？定你戇鳩呀？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T11:40:36.000Z","msg":"下，佢成日係到搞埋曬啲小動作，有次我聽到佢同我條仔阿媽講我喎，仲要成日搬左入去之後成日話要再搬屋，之前仲話想買樓，拎佢小小強積金出黎話比一半首期其他就我條仔供，比啲啲錢想住一世大屋咁都唔戇鳩？"},{"pid":"9ddff0707e3bcd99091b001fc90efd62aa42b61b","tid":2106522,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T11:43:16.000Z","msg":"分手囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e3b7d6a94f130793c10a50d12ab49541be1e914","tid":2106522,"uid":30604,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"quote":{"pid":"c7d96c1440e603a91c3629432bd1c2b2f9c10190","tid":2106522,"uid":222055,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"a21676fed0b50700cd73a1145dfe601094b1bed8","tid":2106522,"uid":30604,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"re